                    <p style="font-size:var(--text-lg);color:var(--text-primary);margin-bottom:var(--space-6)">GroupsMix is a platform dedicated to helping people discover trusted social media groups across WhatsApp, Telegram, Discord, and more.</p>
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>We believe in building safer, more transparent online communities. Our trust-based ranking system ensures that only quality, verified groups reach the top, while scam groups are flagged and removed.</p>
                    <h2>What We Do</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li>&#9989; Curate and verify social media groups</li>
                        <li>&#11088; Community-driven reviews and ratings</li>
                        <li>&#128737;&#65039; Trust scoring and scam protection</li>
                        <li>&#128640; Promotion tools for group owners</li>
                        <li>&#129520; Free tools for group management</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h2>The GXP System</h2>
                    <p>Our GroupsMix Experience Points (GXP) system rewards active community members. Earn points by submitting groups, writing reviews, and engaging with the platform. Higher GXP unlocks levels, badges, and enhanced visibility.</p>
                    <h2>Trust &amp; Safety</h2>
                    <p>Every group goes through our review process. Our trust score algorithm considers verification status, community ratings, report history, and engagement metrics to ensure you always find quality groups.</p>
                    <h2>Contact</h2>
                    <p>Have questions? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> or check our <a href="/faq">FAQ</a>. For comprehensive help, visit the <a href="/support">Support Center</a>.</p>
